Module camstesting
Package camp

Class CampManager

java.lang.Object
camp.CampManager
public class CampManager extends Object
CampManager class is responsible for managing camps and their operations. It maintains a TreeMap of camps and provides methods for adding, removing, and accessing camps.
Since:
24 nov 2023
Version:
1.0
Author:
group1
